title: It's the US Air Force's 72nd birthday — here are 33 photos of it doing what it does best
text:
The US Air Force turns 72 years old on Wednesday. Between the US military's first aircraft purchase in 1909 and the Air Force's official founding on September 18, 1947, the service existed under a number of different designations.

But in the 72 years since since its formation, the Air Force has expanded and perfected its ability to take off, land, lift, transport, strike, and observe from the skies over any part of the world.

Below, you can see some photos of the Air Force and its personnel in action.
description: With 72 years of experience, the aircraft and airmen of US Air Force can be found all over the world, doing all sorts of things.
